SUMMARY:Deadline: Game Design Emerging Talents: Post-Production
DESCRIPTION:Pro Helvetia's Game Design Emerging Talents post-production gra
 nt funds the dissemination and marketing of advanced game-design projects.
  Emerging Talents are studios whose game-design education or company found
 ation dates back less than seven years. Applicants must be legal entities 
 (sole proprietorships accepted if willing to convert). ELIGIBILITY: requir
 es a connection to Switzerland (Swiss citizenship\, or permanent residency
  with regular artistic activity in Switzerland)\; not open to practitioner
 s without a Swiss connection. At least 50 percent of participants must be 
 Swiss citizens or permanent residents whose place of work is in Switzerlan
 d. AMOUNT: up to CHF 20\,000\, plus potential individual coaching. Deadlin
 es twice a year: 1 March (23:59 CET) and 1 September (23:59 CEST). Apply v
 ia the Pro Helvetia portal.\n\nOrganisation: Pro Helvetia (Swiss Arts Coun
 cil)\nLocation: Switzerland-based emerging game studios.\nAward: Up to CHF
  20\,000\, plus potential individual coaching. No application fee.\nDurati
 on: Post-production\, dissemination and marketing phase\; deadlines twice 
 yearly (1 March and 1 September).\n\nMore: https://prohelvetia.ch/en/find-
 support/game-design-emerging-talents-post-production?utm_source=artificial
 nouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://prohelvetia.ch/en/find-support/game-design-emerging-talents-pos
 t-production?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Switzerland-based emerging game studios.
END:VEVENT
